@khelzoneofficial located at N-34, Abul Fazl Enclave Part 1, it’s a fun-filled indoor play area designed to encourage real growth through real play🌷

With the motto “From screen to slides,” the space promotes active, screen-free engagement for children!!

Open every day from 12 PM to 10 PM, Khelzone also offers birthday party bookings and hosts play school/daycare picnics between 12 PM and 5 PM. 
Monthly subscription plans are available with discounts of up to 55%, making it easier than ever to enjoy endless playtime.

latestPosts.alt: Photo by attss | aesthete🦋 on May 09, 2025. May be an image of text that says 'To those glorifying war from the comfort of their homes Do you even know what war really looks like? It's not a victory post. It's not trending hashtags. It's blood. It's fear. It's a mother searching for her child under rubble. It's a soldier writing his last letter home. It's Kashmir crying. Poonch bleeding. Innocent children suffering. And you???? you're cheering. You say it's for the nation, for pride, for revenge, but tell me- What has war ever brought but destruction? What have we ever gained but graves?'.
